      "id": 1,
      "type": "text",
      "title": "About this dashboard",
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "Front-end **NVMe/TCP** view for Pure FlashArrays.\n\n- NVMe/TCP is currently enabled on **sn1-c60-e12-16** and **sn1-x90r2-f07-27** \u2014 R1 panels are empty on other arrays *by design*.\n- **Connection / Connectivity State** (R2) spans **all transports**, not just NVMe; Purity exposes no NVMe-specific session/connection metric.\n- **Array Front-End Performance** (R3) is array-wide and cannot be isolated to NVMe traffic."
      }
    },
